Texts.Chs: 干得漂亮。我想是时候进行下一步了。
Texts.Eng: Great work. I think it's time to move on.

Texts.Chs: ^orange;甲醇^reset;将在各类物品产出以及实验室的壮大中扮演重要的角色。^green;你可以通过萃取原木得到它。
Texts.Eng: ^orange;Methanol^reset; will be useful in the production of a number of goods and eventually get you on track to a masterful laboratory. ^green;You'll find it via wood extraction^reset;.
